WEBVTT

00:00:01.052 --> 00:00:02.715
Joan den urtean,

00:00:02.739 --> 00:00:03.739
familiako hiru kide

00:00:03.739 --> 00:00:05.270
modu basatian erailak izan ziren

00:00:05.270 --> 00:00:06.713
gorrotozko krimen batean.

00:00:08.094 --> 00:00:10.428
Argi dago, niretzat oso zaila dela

00:00:10.452 --> 00:00:12.175
gaur hemen egotea,

00:00:12.199 --> 00:00:13.782
baina Deah, nire nebak,

00:00:13.806 --> 00:00:15.222
Yusor, bere emazteak

00:00:15.246 --> 00:00:16.777
eta Rizan bere ahizpak

00:00:16.801 --> 00:00:18.510
ez didate aukerarik eman.

00:00:19.274 --> 00:00:22.663
Itxaropena dut, hitzaldi hau amaitzerako

00:00:22.687 --> 00:00:25.130
gorrotoaren aurka altxatzera batuko zaretela.

00:00:26.659 --> 00:00:29.746
2014ko abenduaren 27a da:

00:00:29.770 --> 00:00:32.002
nire nebaren ezkontza eguneko goiza.